<InfoPageLayout 
  title="About Us" 
  description="Fresh Wax is an independent UK record label specialising in jungle and drum & bass music. Digital downloads and limited edition vinyl pressings."
>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
    Fresh Wax is an independent UK record label dedicated to preserving and pushing forward the sounds of jungle and drum & bass.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Story</h2>
  <p>
    Born from a deep love of breakbeat culture, Fresh Wax was founded to give a platform to both established artists and emerging talent in the jungle and drum & bass scene. We believe in quality over quantity, carefully curating each release to ensure it meets our standards of excellence.
  </p>
  <p>
    From the rolling basslines of liquid drum & bass to the chopped breaks of classic jungle, we cover the full spectrum of the sound we love. Every release is treated with care, from mastering to artwork, ensuring our artists' music is presented in the best possible way.
  </p>

  <h2>What We Do</h2>
  <h3>Digital Releases</h3>
  <p>
    High-quality digital downloads in multiple formats including WAV, FLAC, and MP3. Our digital releases are available immediately upon release, giving you instant access to the freshest tracks.
  </p>

  <h3>Vinyl Pressings</h3>
  <p>
    Limited edition vinyl pressings for the collectors and DJs who appreciate the warmth and authenticity of wax. Each vinyl release is pressed in limited quantities, making them true collector's items.
  </p>

  <h3>Artist Development</h3>
  <p>
    We work closely with our artists to develop their sound and reach. From providing feedback on productions to helping with promotion and distribution, we're invested in our artists' success.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Quality First</strong> – We never compromise on audio quality or presentation</li>
    <li><strong>Artist Focused</strong> – Fair deals and transparent communication with all our artists</li>
    <li><strong>Community Driven</strong> – Supporting the wider jungle and drum & bass community</li>
    <li><strong>Independent Spirit</strong> – Staying true to the underground while growing sustainably</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Get Involved</h2>
  <p>
    Whether you're an artist looking for a home for your music, a DJ seeking fresh tracks, or a fan of the sound, we'd love to hear from you.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>For demo submissions:</strong> <a href="mailto:demos@freshwax.co.uk">demos@freshwax.co.uk</a><br>
    <strong>General enquiries:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@freshwax.co.uk">info@freshwax.co.uk</a>
  </p>

  <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-100 border-l-4 border-black">
    <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Support the Underground</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-0">
      Every purchase directly supports independent artists and helps keep the jungle and drum & bass scene alive. Thank you for being part of the Fresh Wax family.
    </p>
  </div>
</InfoPageLayout>